{"id":"drawer-of-water","term":"Drawer of water","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>(<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Deuteronomy 29:11\">Deut. 29:11</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Joshua 9:21\">Josh. 9:21</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Joshua 9:23\">23</a>), a servile employment to which the Gibeonites were condemned.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Deuteronomy 29:11","Joshua 9:21","Joshua 9:23"]}